OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1774026671
OL,3,CFormer police officer sentenced to 24
OL,4,Cyears in prison for multiple sex
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FWarning: This article contains details
OL,8,Freaders may find distressing
OL,10,FA former volunteer Metropolitan Police
OL,11,Fofficer who raped and sexually
OL,12,Fassaulted a child has been jailed for
OL,13,F24 years.
OL,15,FJames Bubb, who now identifies as a
OL,16,Fwoman named Gwyn Samuels, groomed one
OL,17,Fof two victims online before sexually
OL,18,Fassaulting her when she was just 12
OL,19,Fyears old.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1774026671
OL,3,CFormer police officer sentenced to 24
OL,4,Cyears in prison for multiple sex
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FSamuels was found guilty of raping and
OL,8,Fsexually assaulting the girl after a
OL,9,Ftrial last summer.
OL,11,FThe 28-year-old, from Chesham in
OL,12,FBuckinghamshire, was also found guilty
OL,13,Fof raping a woman after meeting her
OL,14,Fonline while posing as a 16-year-old
OL,15,Fgirl.
OL,17,FAll charges took place between January
OL,18,F1, 2018, and April 2, 2024.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1774026671
OL,3,CFormer police officer sentenced to 24
OL,4,Cyears in prison for multiple sex
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FThe former special constable was
OL,8,Fsentenced to a total of 32 years, made
OL,9,Fup of 24 years' imprisonment and a
OL,10,Ffurther eight years on extended
OL,11,Flicence, at Aylesbury Crown Court on
OL,12,FFriday.
OL,14,FSentencing the defendant, Judge
OL,15,FJonathan Cooper said Samuels "abused
OL,16,Fthe most intimate trust of your
OL,17,Fvictims" in "a campaign of abuse
OL,18,Fagainst each that was intended to
OL,19,Fbreak their will entirely".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1774026671
OL,3,CFormer police officer sentenced to 24
OL,4,Cyears in prison for multiple sex
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FThroughout the trial, the defendant
OL,8,Fwas referred to by their biological
OL,9,Fsex, but during the first sentencing
OL,10,Fhearing last week, the judge said that
OL,11,Fsince they have transitioned, they
OL,12,Fshould be known by their new identity
OL,13,Fof Gwyn Samuels.
OL,15,FThe judge said he understands the
OL,16,Fdefendant, who has been in the male
OL,17,Fprison estate while in custody, will
OL,18,Fremain there.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1774026671
OL,3,CFormer police officer sentenced to 24
OL,4,Cyears in prison for multiple sex
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,F"The key point is that you are a very
OL,8,Fsignificant risk to women," Judge
OL,9,FCooper said. "This is not predicated
OL,10,Fon your trans status, but on your
OL,11,Fcriminal status."
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/11
