OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1774026671
OL,3,CFormer police officer sentenced to 24
OL,4,Cyears in prison for multiple sex
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FAmersham Law Courts heard Samuels met
OL,8,Ftheir first victim on the and chat
OL,9,Froulette site Omegle in 2018 before
OL,10,Fmeeting in person for the first time
OL,11,Fat a Christian festival a few months
OL,12,Flater.
OL,14,FThe girl said the defendant looked
OL,15,F"paranoid" when they were with her and
OL,16,Fshe was being "hidden" when they were
OL,17,Fin public together, telling police her
OL,18,Ffestival colour-coded child wristband
OL,19,Fwas clearly on show.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1774026671
OL,3,CFormer police officer sentenced to 24
OL,4,Cyears in prison for multiple sex
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FIn relation to this first victim,
OL,8,FSamuels was found guilty of one count
OL,9,Fof raping a child under 13, one count
OL,10,Fof sexual activity with a child, one
OL,11,Fcount of assault of a child under 13
OL,12,Fby penetration, and one count of
OL,13,Fassault by penetration.
OL,15,FThe court heard the officer raped
OL,16,Ftheir second victim, a woman who had
OL,17,Fjust turned 18 when she met the
OL,18,Fdefendant.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1774026671
OL,3,CFormer police officer sentenced to 24
OL,4,Cyears in prison for multiple sex
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FThe second victim, whom we are calling
OL,8,FTyler, said the pair started an on-and-
OL,9,Foff relationship that spanned from
OL,10,FJanuary 2018 to February 2023.
OL,12,FThe relationship quickly turned
OL,13,F"distressing", Tyler said, adding that
OL,14,Fthey were often not allowed to leave
OL,15,FSamuels' flat.
OL,17,F"It was very difficult," Tyler said,
OL,18,F"I wish I got out sooner."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1774026671
OL,3,CFormer police officer sentenced to 24
OL,4,Cyears in prison for multiple sex
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FIn a personal address to Samuels'
OL,8,Fvictims after the defendant left
OL,9,Fcourt, the judge told the victims:
OL,10,F"Over time, I hope the fact that you
OL,11,Fare survivors of abuse is ultimately
OL,12,Fmore important to your future lives
OL,13,Fthan the fact you were victims of it.
OL,15,F"I have to acknowledge that your
OL,16,Fordeal at the hands of this defendant
OL,17,Fwas made infinitely more challenging
OL,18,Fby your experiences of the criminal
OL,19,Fjustice system.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1774026671
OL,3,CFormer police officer sentenced to 24
OL,4,Cyears in prison for multiple sex
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,F"There were delays and frustrations at
OL,8,Fevery turn. At various times you felt
OL,9,Fthat power was in the hands of the
OL,10,Fdefendant. Ultimately, power was in
OL,11,Fyour own hands, and particularly in
OL,12,Fyour own voices.
OL,14,F"The power of your evidence was heard
OL,15,Fand recognised by the jury in this
OL,16,Fcase."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
